{"tid":2384822,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［水落石出］女督察曾問大肚婆家姐：「你係咪仇警？」","createTime":"2021-01-28T17:22:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-28T19:07:18.000Z","uid":219007,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"bb5f92f0a679d560b96fdb554ca0872f750a8256","tid":2384822,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T17:22:23.000Z","msg":"劉女士說，妹妹留院期間徹夜難眠，她亦一度被拒與妹妹見面，「差人話因為我個妹係犯人，叫我唔好阻差辦公」。劉為妹妹辦理入院手續時，亦有兩名警員陪同，她稱其中一名女督察曾問她：「你係咪仇警？」劉女士大惑不解，強調全家人對警察無敵意。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/港聞/article/20210124/s00002/1611427662983/遇截查被指不合作-涉阻差被捕-孕婦疑被警辱罵拖行-早產嬰入icu?fbclid=IwAR17zMERbVpIvlwgyclWtap8yjZt5MEsDTPWYSUeTGsz_hchMHei6t9OJps\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20210124%2Fs00002%2F1611427662983%2F%E9%81%87%E6%88%AA%E6%9F%A5%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%88%E4%BD%9C-%E6%B6%89%E9%98%BB%E5%B7%AE%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95-%E5%AD%95%E5%A9%A6%E7%96%91%E8%A2%AB%E8%AD%A6%E8%BE%B1%E7%BD%B5%E6%8B%96%E8%A1%8C-%E6%97%A9%E7%94%A2%E5%AC%B0%E5%85%A5icu%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR17zMERbVpIvlwgyclWtap8yjZt5MEsDTPWYSUeTGsz_hchMHei6t9OJps&d=YX1qj72dVL8lCt3J0nVEUhvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=0c2f8b3a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20210124%2Fs00002%2F1611427662983%2F%E9%81%87%E6%88%AA%E6%9F%A5%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%88%E4%BD%9C-%E6%B6%89%E9%98%BB%E5%B7%AE%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95-%E5%AD%95%E5%A9%A6%E7%96%91%E8%A2%AB%E8%AD%A6%E8%BE%B1%E7%BD%B5%E6%8B%96%E8%A1%8C-%E6%97%A9%E7%94%A2%E5%AC%B0%E5%85%A5icu%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR17zMERbVpIvlwgyclWtap8yjZt5MEsDTPWYSUeTGsz_hchMHei6t9OJps&h=ee157610\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/pns/港聞/article/20210124/s00002/1611427662983/遇截查被指不合作-涉阻差被捕-孕婦疑被警辱罵拖行-早產嬰入icu?fbclid=IwAR17zMERbVpIvlwgyclWtap8yjZt5MEsDTPWYSUeTGsz_hchMHei6t9OJps</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n成件事好明顯係因為個藍絲大肚婆杞人憂天（本身好多大肚婆都係咁好正常，陀住個B所以驚呢樣驚果樣，怕疫情健康等等），所以喺班popo面前表現得有啲唔合作。 於是班popo影射左個大肚婆係仇警曱甴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />就打鳩佢鎖鳩佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n比着前幾年發生呢啲事，所有媒體狂屌。 過咗2019年之後冚家剷鵪哂鶉啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 免得跌入政治漩渦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  依家個社會仲要靠班popo頂住冇得蹆，唔可以蝕咗道氣，所以嗰老母要有心理準備唯有當生少件啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c15518ccaa3696b528e535527a7c26c2dd6d272e","tid":2384822,"uid":44074,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T17:23:49.000Z","msg":"陰公🥺🥺"},{"pid":"c10cc8205e7a88a6e1548341fa7d5bd52e6af212","tid":2384822,"uid":271516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T17:24:54.000Z","msg":"精神分裂"},{"pid":"d28e4d9829bd1ce9eebe9ca879f367769e4248cf","tid":2384822,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T17:38:11.000Z","msg":"係，咁點？<br />\n係唔係要拉埋？"},{"pid":"b9915067758af44996bbeddfd08a071c71c57d9c","tid":2384822,"uid":179409,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-